:3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5dac5a65c5f05823a6ae80d200e216e65e26c4f1","tid":522632,"uid":131323,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:04:19.000Z","msg":"冇文化真可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T19:08:32.000Z","msg":"講d論點出黎聽下，淨係講一句垃圾說話無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無文化既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35eea413ebc9eb33fa42411749a3a3aca4735e5d","tid":522632,"uid":44044,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T19:19:59.000Z","msg":"但係你唔覺死刑佢地好著數咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死一死就解決左件事<br />\n真 終生監禁直到佢死<br />\n等佢幾十年無自由係監度等死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8157b4699932f7fb71d272699a712dbcfc3be79f","tid":522632,"uid":150831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T19:21:33.000Z","msg":"支持恢復死刑 反正平常人正正常常都唔會犯事 但好多虐殺 謀殺呢啲 死刑我覺得好合理 憑咩殺左人仍然可以安安樂樂係監倉過下半世 不過萬一死刑被權力支配就好危險"},{"pid":"0c62b45a02409436bf1d394c36697cfacd11203e","tid":522632,"uid":37666,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T19:21:47.000Z","msg":"死刑變當權者工具點算先<br />\n判錯你比番條命人呀<br />\n終身監禁鎖佢係黑房五六十年仲好啦<br />\n所以要變就應該變個監獄<br />\n最好似泰國個啲<br />\n你犯咁大罪居然想比佢一死了之咁便宜佢"},{"pid":"7c4926e0b2868d4ade383337e07b6bc1dc8a5eb5","tid":522632,"uid":37666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T19:26:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇文化真可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地諗得太直接啫唔係冇送化<br />\n下下話殺 係簡單快捷<br />\n不過係需用於啲落後地方<br />\n好似中國印度啲人多到咁<br />\n唔用死刑嚇佢地好難統治既"},{"pid":"d05993783ad92aec549e55c17fd48b973bd30d7b","tid":522632,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T19:28:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇文化真可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地諗得太直接啫唔係冇<span style=\"color: red;\">文</span>化<br />\n下下話殺 係簡單快捷<br />\n不過係需用於啲落後地方<br />\n好似中國印度啲人多到咁<br />\n唔用死刑嚇佢地好難統治既</blockquote>"},{"pid":"376c6d51363d5f958ed04940efc7124610a7b3ec","tid":522632,"uid":103230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T19:48:06.000Z","msg":"一日冇民主<br />\n死刑只係當權者既工具"},{"pid":"03f41bc9b8b0b8a0858770c81bab84f9f7f0393c","tid":522632,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T22:27:32.000Z","msg":"唔支持, 因為所謂肉刑都係不可回頭的刑罰"},{"pid":"55f75636921498e8f860b7ef6f8259de01963bab","tid":522632,"uid":20916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T22:32:22.000Z","msg":"死刑同終身監禁既阻嚇性唔會差好遠。平時都話坐一世=玩撚完，但一同死刑比就突然變左安安樂樂坐半世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b511f98e5493cb9b846e5dc5d6fc39a4ee4adf","tid":522632,"uid":78188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T22:37:06.000Z","msg":"支持酷刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死刑只會益撚左班人"},{"pid":"bbe3497f871dd6f949a173573d304666d170eab3","tid":522632,"uid":50328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T22:37:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04f0ab797b6bc5c97d938de7551a26665f2b1a23","tid":522632,"uid":148279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T23:00:44.000Z","msg":"先不論政治，淨係講死刑<br />\n如果著重係人權方面，當啲人犯左殺人放火嘅罪行，我地仲需唔需要當佢係人呢。另外，死刑執行後，的確無得挽救，意味死刑係要係證據確鑿嘅情況之下先可以實行。<br />\n我覺得係有一個完善系統之下嘅死刑係好事黎"},{"pid":"ce57504713825e7f3aec89f6764a5a2dc88a7410","tid":522632,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T00:36:43.000Z","msg":"支那加死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你覺得咩人會被判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9560aaff55a06b08d61dc4a05f4d3d0635fc49","tid":522632,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03f41bc9b8b0b8a0858770c81bab84f9f7f0393c","tid":52